{"tid":496304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府藉研綠色交通為名反轉大嶼山","createTime":"2017-12-11T14:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T14:43:29.000Z","uid":144018,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"068faf6114b52da1c7a8d767ee12a3ed0e68d067","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"//《星島日報》獨家報道，當局早前公布《可持續大嶼藍圖》後，開始進行深化設計。據《星島日報》了解，為加強大澳的旅客接待能力，政府顧問最新決定探討以輕軌替代道路，貫通東涌與大澳兩個地點，以配合推動綠色交通的發展方向。有地區人士估計，以駕空方式興建的輕軌，有助減少砍伐樹木或避免進行填海，較在地面興建連接道路和早前提出以纜車接駁至大澳的構想更為可行。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1086167/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1086167%2F&d=FbdMh5f%2FKkb97iUAaJbbUl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=81fb671b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1086167%2F&h=8b7e38cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1086167/</a><br />\n<br />\n//據《星島日報》了解，當局在進行深入研究將會正式評估在合適的地點，興建碼頭設施的需要及進行初步可行性研究，初步有機會選揀選的地點包括長沙及二澳一帶，藉以輔助往來康樂及旅遊發展項目的陸路交通//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1086176/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1086176%2F&d=FbdMh5f%2FKkb97iUAaJbbUl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=cff48d79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1086176%2F&h=7d42c2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1086176/</a><br />\n<br />\n//為推動大嶼山的旅遊業和本土經濟，運輸署於兩年前開始放寬進入嶼南路的限制，鑑於配額經常用盡，《星島日報》報道指，署方正考慮「加碼」，讓平日以「自駕遊」方式進入大嶼山私家車名額倍增至五十個，旅遊巴士限額亦增至五十個。地區人士認為，若能增加「自駕遊」配額，可望產生「分流」效果，讓小商戶平日也能增加收入//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1086170/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1086170%2F&d=FbdMh5f%2FKkb97iUAaJbbUl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=61b0d5dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1086170%2F&h=f2023779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1086170/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府死咬住大嶼山唔放，誓要搞到大嶼山天翻地覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54811208d70c4a2733bf77894826d3672a5d2efb","tid":496304,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"On9咁撚多山路上落小站仲要搞條路軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0949b12dbe4be99a6f5238cdd06f921b55a8445c","tid":496304,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote></blockquote><br />\n當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f31ae9032ec6f3e959adbad60fa2976d36b8e47","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9咁撚多山路上落小站仲要搞條路軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果無估錯條走線會係依家既東澳古道<br />\n一路都話想起多條路入去，但一路都搞唔掂環評<br />\n家下就搞輕鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad31145c52de0468a5a56a8ae8bbc348d989b358","tid":496304,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56b163895a2dc66f1b127454ab58fba4070ba27","tid":496304,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"講個笑話: 架空輕鐵易過架空纜車"},{"pid":"c4e913e61bb7ebe6b2763bfe4052e6b67692fa3c","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"l