個technical feasibility report講咩先。同埋有啲大澳居民同地主分分鐘想要新馬路多過鐵路先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會擺渡輪先既原因係係依個情況（東涌至大澳）本身就有渡輪接駁，只係依家無好好利用<br />\n而帶嚟既影響相對比較細<br />\n依家情況係巴士做唔切，渡輪又未發揮到應有作用<br />\n所以我覺得應該先搞好渡輪，善用現有資源<br />\n同埋有個諗法就係架空鐵路起咗就無得返轉頭，但渡輪如果唔夠人都可以調去其他航線<br />\n<br />\n最驚就係依家個政府話要起就起乜都唔理，巴別塔都話起到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f03d47217bcbd14e251ad2c1cac8bfc55f02da","tid":496304,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"最後架車反左落山"},{"pid":"4133c37904c8416dd2f0743182b4589c36cecdcb","tid":496304,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:36:27.000Z","msg":"起地鐵咪得囉仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf64c2f5ee95e8781e0e07a026468c0849afa87e","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起地鐵咪得囉仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20218f41ec4f4717e4dee85667f5cc9b6c73ec7","tid":496304,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"最大利益者應該係魚蛋灣大地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df452519727f2c11d1fe67023d322166c2e8a9dc","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最大利益者應該係魚蛋灣大地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起去大澳點解會係愉景灣得益最大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b58bb63bfa21b9fbce0050b214c98e0cf3726c6","tid":496304,"uid":47355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"先利申，小弟係做依行<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打都講渡輪<br />\n其實唔少feasibility study都有要求研究用渡輪做連接的可能性<br />\n唔少study其實用渡輪就可以解決唔少traffic問題，可能可以起少d infrastructure, 令到單野快d上馬&hellip;<br />\n不過因為根本就冇operator肯做，所以好多都唔成事，去到pe stage大家都唔會見到有渡輪依個option<br />\n話番轉頭，就算有operator肯做，試諗下要搭完船同搭多程車，車錢都唔少野，冇政策support好難鼓勵人搭船"},{"pid":"c7e732a0fe6e74ef171a2a68e67b7e5ed7205f59","tid":496304,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ced3f78c6d18c83ab72803c4ddcccfcf0c57921","tid":496304,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點計唔打風既日子都比打風多<br />\n同埋因為打風唔完全唔掂海路，有D斬腳趾避沙蟲Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實香港周邊海面算唔算繁忙</blockquote><br />\n你算有啲Engineering sense.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你只要答我EIAO有咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環 境 影 響 評 估 條 例 (第 499 章)<br />\n<br />\n本 條 例 旨 在 就 評 估 某 些 工 程 項 目 及 提 議 對 環 境 的 影 響 ， 就 保 護 環 境 和 就 附 帶 事 宜 訂 定 條 文 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊樣環評易過就做邊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c711d3e88358d28f3eda620e1c71af823db25bc3","tid":496304,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604ab35991c973c89388d781764717e1a7ef5bca","tid":496304,"uid":47355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先利申，小弟係做依行<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打都講渡輪<br />\n其實唔少feasibility study都有要求研究用渡輪做連接的可能性<br />\n唔少study其實用渡輪就可以解決唔少traffic問題，可能可以起少d infrastructure, 令到單野快d上馬&hellip;<br />\n不過因為根本就冇operator肯做，所以好多都唔成事，去到pe stage大家都唔會見到有渡輪依個option<br />\n話番轉頭，就算有operator肯做，試諗下要搭完船同搭多程車，車錢都唔少野，冇政策support好難鼓勵人搭船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而認為可以加強現有東涌大澳渡輪服務<br />\n仲有改善東涌碼頭同港鐵站/公共交通交匯處嘅接駁</blockquote><br />\n都冇咁多人搭，好多時都係車空氣，只係假日先多人搭<br />\n先唔計錢，冇人搭，班次就會少，班次少難就時間d人就唔搭，一個loop&hellip;<br />\n東涌大澳渡輪只係一個例子去講香港渡輪有幾難做，東涌大澳仲有得做係因為有假日客，而且佢係沙螺灣唯一交通，同埋tmclkl仲未開"},{"pid":"4c768590864926332631a10019c9fc72b56769b6","tid":496304,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先利申，小弟係做依行<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打都講渡輪<br />\n其實唔少feasibility study都有要求研究用渡輪做連接的可能性<br />\n唔少study其實用渡輪就可以解決唔少traffic問題，可能可以起少d infrastructure, 令到單野快d上馬&hellip;<br />\n不過因為根本就冇operator肯做，所以好多都唔成事，去到pe stage大家都唔會見到有渡輪依個option<br />\n話番轉頭，就算有operator肯做，試諗下要搭完船同搭多程車，車錢都唔少野，冇政策support好難鼓勵人搭船</blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510a7f00da35ec0989f491378a1d7e47a82430bb","tid":496304,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你只要答我EIAO有咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環 境 影 響 評 估 條 例 (第 499 章)<br />\n<br />\n本 條 例 旨 在 就 評 估 某 些 工 程 項 目 及 提 議 對 環 境 的 影 響 ， 就 保 護 環 境 和 就 附 帶 事 宜 訂 定 條 文 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請巴打明言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如我地諗下點解要架空鐵路？有咩好處？  同相對嘅交通工具有咩唔同？<br />\n個environmental impact 會係點？ 對當地交通，經濟有咩好處？<br />\nCost &amp; benefit matrix 係點？<br />\nEIAO有咩成份？邊樣選擇會好啲？<br />\n對成個香港嘅long term同short term macro and microeconmics 嘅影響？從sustainability 睇會點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為架空鐵路無疑可以提供一個巴士更快捷、更大載客量、更環保既接駁選擇亦有助改善大澳對外交通，此舉可以吸引更多人前往大澳<br />\n但按照現時既走線估計，架空鐵路無可避免咁會影響到大嶼山北岸既天然海岸線同埋附近既郊野公園，亦會做成視覺既影響<br />\n而好似上面咁講起好後會吸引更加人入大澳，大澳可唔可以容納更多人係一個疑問<br />\n更重要係政府會唔會借起架空鐵路為名，借機大肆破壞沿線環境<br />\n<br />\n就暫時咁多選項，我會咁排<br />\n渡輪&gt;架空鐵路&gt;起新馬路<br />\n<br />\n非專業性人士，純個人見解<br />\n不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條港珠澳已經破壞哂啦<br />\n渡輪其實呢家已經有條<br />\n大澳 &gt; 唔記得咩名 &gt; 東涌 &gt; 屯門"},{"pid":"fe70d825a04cdcd297714b7d38bbbad3ce63d239","tid":496304,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c159f41adea50545112f6479d2759b78dcae3765","tid":496304,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"我反而想東澳古道拓闊起單車徑多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過ff下算喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3ab312f50f647fa02100f41ab56c3f50b4f9fe","tid":496304,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先利申，小弟係做依行<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打都講渡輪<br />\n其實唔少feasibility study都有要求研究用渡輪做連接的可能性<br />\n唔少study其實用渡輪就可以解決唔少traffic問題，可能可以起少d infrastructure, 令到單野快d上馬&hellip;<br />\n不過因為根本就冇operator肯做，所以好多都唔成事，去到pe stage大家都唔會見到有渡輪依個option<br />\n話番轉頭，就算有operator肯做，試諗下要搭完船同搭多程車，車錢都唔少野，冇政策support好難鼓勵人搭船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而認為可以加強現有東涌大澳渡輪服務<br />\n仲有改善東涌碼頭同港鐵站/公共交通交匯處嘅接駁</blockquote><br />\n都冇咁多人搭，好多時都係車空氣，只係假日先多人<br />\n先唔計錢，冇人搭，班次就會少，班次少難就時間d人就唔搭，一個loop&hellip;<br />\n東涌大澳渡輪只係一個例子去講香港渡輪有幾難做，東涌大澳仲有得做係因為有假日客，而且佢係沙螺灣唯一交通，同埋tmclkl仲未開</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實會唔會考慮剩係假日加密渡輪班次?</blockquote><br />\n佢依家都有加密<br />\n講到尾都係錢，有錢賺佢多多都開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真，依個project 明顯就係想放多d 人去大澳，果到d infrastructure頂唔頂到呢"},{"pid":"35217434ad89e28e0bbf67bae0fe34684699ef44","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先利申，小弟係做依行<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打都講渡輪<br />\n其實唔少feasibility study都有要求研究用渡輪做連接的可能性<br />\n唔少study其實用渡輪就可以解決唔少traffic問題，可能可以起少d infrastructure, 令到單野快d上馬&hellip;<br />\n不過因為根本就冇operator肯做，所以好多都唔成事，去到pe stage大家都唔會見到有渡輪依個option<br />\n話番轉頭，就算有operator肯做，試諗下要搭完船同搭多程車，車錢都唔少野，冇政策support好難鼓勵人搭船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n受教了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實大家都知個問題係邊，只係政府闊佬爛理所以先搞到渡輪發展咁差<br />\n睇返依家咁多條渡輪航線，有邊條路係蝕要政府貼紙先維到皮<br />\n<br />\n同埋我都覺得同大家對渡輪既印象有關，就係大家都覺得搭渡輪會慢過搭車<br />\n自自然然大家都去哂搭車<br />\n個人認為要係速度同載客量做平衡好重要<br />\n一方面可以令大家覺得渡輪既速度唔會慢過車，另一方面營運商成本又唔會太高"},{"pid":"33b0551f5ff886e03fecc883f30f99c9db540c75","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>先利申，小弟係做依行<br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打都講渡輪<br />\n其實唔少feasibility study都有要求研究用渡輪做連接的可能性<br />\n唔少study其實用渡輪就可以解決唔少traffic問題，可能可以起少d infrastructure, 令到單野快d上馬&hellip;<br />\n不過因為根本就冇operator肯做，所以好多都唔成事，去到pe stage大家都唔會見到有渡輪依個option<br />\n話番轉頭，就算有operator肯做，試諗下要搭完船同搭多程車，車錢都唔少野，冇政策support好難鼓勵人搭船</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而認為可以加強現有東涌大澳渡輪服務<br />\n仲有改善東涌碼頭同港鐵站/公共交通交匯處嘅接駁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英雄所見略同<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f302f665357be90b4625589ca1c12a695d36bf8","tid":496304,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點計唔打風既日子都比打風多<br />\n同埋因為打風唔完全唔掂海路，有D斬腳趾避沙蟲Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實香港周邊海面算唔算繁忙</blockquote><br />\n你算有啲Engineering sense.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n求賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你只要答我EIAO有咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環 境 影 響 評 估 條 例 (第 499 章)<br />\n<br />\n本 條 例 旨 在 就 評 估 某 些 工 程 項 目 及 提 議 對 環 境 的 影 響 ， 就 保 護 環 境 和 就 附 帶 事 宜 訂 定 條 文 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><